 grub-extras (utilies to be used with grub)
 
 This package includes:
 grubconfig, script to install and configure grub  in a newly installed
 system at end of installation, can also be  used in a running system,
 and the associated wrapper script setup.grubconfig.
 update-grub is a wrapper script to grub-mkconfig.
 This package also provides files to make an USB boot stick allowing to 
 boot an installed Slint system and other OS on the same machine, mostly
 borrowed to Slackware, thanks to Patrick Volkerding.
